slide:
Invariant Property Types

Covariant Returns and Contravariant Parameters — Levi Morrison
https://wiki.php.net/rfc/covariant-returns-and-contravariant-parameters —

typed properties are invariant


<?php
class 🌐sphere {}
class 🌏planet extends 🌐sphere {}

class Bakery
{
	public 🌐sphere $temperature;
}

class Patisserie extends Bakery
{
	public 🌏planet $temperature;
}
?>


Fatal error: Type of Patisserie::$temperature must be 🌐sphere (as in class Bakery)

Property types are *in-variant*:
~they can *not* represent a more specific or a more broad type~
